source.name: Natural  Hazards Image Discovery Tool
source.description: Natural Hazards Image Discovery Tool from NOAA's National Geophysical Data Center provides search and discovery; descriptive and location information; and download access to over 1000 images of the damage from natural hazards.Collection-level ISO metadata exist for the collections; metadata for web service in development in coordination with the NOC IOCM and CMSP efforts.
